      <p class="- topic/p ">After you log in, explore everything the community has to offer by clicking the “Get started” tab in the top navigation menu.</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">If you’re ready to jump right into training, there are two ways to access the Power Learning Center:</p>
      <ul class="- topic/ul ">
         <li class="- topic/li ">On the home page, click the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">“Learning center”</uicontrol> tile</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">In the top navigation, click the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">“Learn”</uicontrol> tab and then click
               <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol "> “Learning center”</uicontrol> on the dropdown menu</li>
